  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As an undercover cop you will infiltrate a dangerous criminal organisation and embark on an extraordinary mission to bring it down. As a teacher, your mission is to stop the gang's activities at the school and in the neighbourhood! Depending on your choices, the story will take shape, relationships will develop and outcomes will change. The decisions are entirely up to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >               </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tCreated by a solo developer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\t3 Chapter Story (High School, University, Municipality Building)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tEach Chapter has more than one ending</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•       Your choices affect the story</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872270/extras/ef7896ada49872b2a86335aed6017917.avif?t=1733596781\" width=650 height=250 /></span>               </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BE A GOOD TEACHER</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tTake classes and earn money by lecturing to your students.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tGive exams to your students and earn money when you get the exam grades right.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tInteract with them and mould your relationship level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872270/extras/327ba1f1d9d54743a38aa76aabd4c892.avif?t=1733596781\" width=650 height=250 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BE A BAD TEACHER</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tKeep your relationship with the gang good.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tGive extra point to the bum students.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tTake the assault and battery missions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872270/extras/ca43f7aa460e03c075736b8b4db27479.avif?t=1733596781\" width=650 height=250 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WATCH YOUR CHOICES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tYour conversations with people will affect the rest of the story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tArrest anyone you don't trust or suspect! Or infiltrate the gang.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
